                                <strong style="font-size:0.48rem; color:rgb(236, 16, 16);margin-right: -.2rem;">添加朋友</strong>
                                <span style="font-size:0.48rem;">→选择</span>
                                <strong style="font-size:0.48rem; color:rgb(234, 16, 16);margin-left: -.2rem">公众号</strong>
                                <span style="font-size:0.48rem;"></span>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <span style="font-size:0.48rem;">3、长按粘贴</span>
                                <strong style="font-size:0.48rem; color:rgb(239, 9, 9);margin: 0 -.2rem;"><%= gonghao_id %></strong>
                                <span style="font-size:0.48rem;">→关注</span>
                                <strong style="font-size:0.48rem; color:rgb(239, 9, 9);margin: 0 -.2rem;"><%= name %></strong>
                                <span style=font-size:0.48rem;">即可继续阅读！</span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <img style="margin-top: .8rem" src="<%= finalImg %>" alt="">
        <p class="company"><%= company %></p>
        <div class="popup-wrap">
            <div class="popup-box" onclick="return false;">
                <div class="title">
                    <div class="success-icon"></div>
                    <span class="notice-title">复制成功</span></div>
                <div class="content-tips">您已成功复制微信号，是否立即跳转到微信搜索该微信号？</div>
                <!--<div class="btn popup-cancle" style="display:inline-block">取消</div>-->
                <div class="btn popup-close">确定</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div style="display:none" data-author="mingxingshuo">
    <% if(typeof statisticsUrl1 != "undefined") { %>
        <%- statisticsUrl1 %>
    <% } %>
</div>
